OL,6,FConservative leadership hopeful Kemi
OL,7,FBadenoch has insisted she does
OL,8,F"believe in maternity pay" after
OL,9,Fpreviously describing it as
OL,10,F"excessive".
OL,12,FBadenoch's comments on Sunday sparked
OL,13,Fa backlash after she appeared to
OL,14,Fcriticise statutory maternity pay,
OL,15,Fsaying the government is doing "too
OL,16,Fmuch".
OL,18,FShe has since appeared to row back on
OL,19,Fher remarks, posting on X that she
OL,20,Fdoes support maternity pay.
